"title": "8795: persecution, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8795: persecution, nature of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Persecution by the world and secular powers is a likely consequence of faith. Scripture identifies a number of potential sources of such persistent harassment.</p>\n<h2>Persecution is characteristic of this world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:2\">PSA 10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:6\">AMO 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:9\">AMO 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:1\">AMO 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:6-Hab1:11\">HAB 1:6–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:8\">REV 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:7-Rev9:10\">REV 9:7–9:10</a></p>\n<h2>Satan is the arch-persecutor of the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:6-Job2:7\">JOB 2:6–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:1\">ZEC 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:3-Luke22:4\">LUK 22:3–22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:13\">REV 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>The agencies of persecution</h2>\n<h3>The world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:18\">JHN 15:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:13\">1JN 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:7\">MRK 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:18\">JHN 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:19\">JHN 15:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:14\">JHN 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">ACT 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14-1Thess2:15\">1TH 2:14–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a></p>\n<h3>Earthly governments</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:9\">MRK 13:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:2\">1KI 19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:1\">NEH 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:9\">NEH 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:6\">EST 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:161\">PSA 119:161</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:13-Dan3:17\">DAN 3:13–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:17\">MAT 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:1-Acts12:3\">ACT 12:1–12:3</a></p>\n<h3>Religious authorities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:13-1Thess2:16\">1TH 2:13–2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:8\">JER 26:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:12-Amos7:13\">AMO 7:12–7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:34-Matt23:37\">MAT 23:34–23:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:27-Acts4:29\">ACT 4:27–4:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:17-Acts5:18\">ACT 5:17–5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:4\">ACT 22:4</a>REV <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:7\">13:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:15\">REV 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:6\">REV 17:6</a></p>\n<h3>Family and friends</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:36\">MAT 10:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:6\">MIC 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8\">GEN 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:21\">MAT 10:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:21\">MRK 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:29\">GAL 4:29</a></p>\n<h2>The experience of persecution</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:14\">1SA 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps59:1-Ps59:4\">PSA 59:1–59:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:1-Ps64:4\">PSA 64:1–64:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:8-2Cor4:12\">2CO 4:8–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:26\">2CO 11:23–11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:32-Heb11:38\">HEB 11:32–11:38</a></p>\n<h2>Believers must expect persecution</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:21\">MAT 13:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:4\">1TH 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>Persecution is part of the tribulation of the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:7-Matt24:10\">MAT 24:7–24:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3-2Thess2:4\">2TH 2:3–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:11\">REV 6:11</a></p>\n<h2>Persecution is sometimes part of God's judgment on his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:16-Lam4:19\">LAM 4:16–4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:22-Jer6:26\">JER 6:22–6:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:26-Jer32:29\">JER 32:26–32:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:5-Jer39:10\">JER 39:5–39:10</a></p>",
